ary":"當Alice Forster於1400年出生在英國史洛普爾卡斯特萊-普爾維爾巴時，她的父親Richard Forster33歲，母親Elizabeth De Buckton28歲。她於1424年與Sir John Knight在英國史洛普爾史福斯波利結婚。他們至少是2個兒子的父母。她去世於1507年6月19日在英國越可爾克雷文享年107歲。"},"zh-hans":{"1400–19 June 1507":"1400年–1507年6月19日","1400–1507":"1400年–1507年","1400–1491":"1400年–1491年","1420–1499":"1420年–1499年","1427–1516":"1427年–1516年","1368–Male":"1368年–殁","1372–1450":"1372年–1450年","1450":"1450年","1372":"1372年","1491":"1491年","1424":"1424年","1368":"1368年","1400":"1400年","1499":"1499年","1455":"1455年","1420":"1420年","19 June 1507":"1507年6月19日","1507":"1507年","1516":"1516年","1427":"1427年","Craven District, North Yorkshire, England":"英国越可爾克雷文","Castle Pulverbatch, Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England":"英国英格兰史洛普爾卡斯特萊-普爾維爾巴","Northamptonshire, England":"英国諾薩普頓史爾","Castle-Pulverbatch, Shropshire, England":"英国史洛普爾卡斯特萊-普爾維爾巴","Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England":"英国史洛普爾史福斯波利","lifeSummary":"当Alice Forster于1400年出生在英国史洛普爾卡斯特萊-普爾維爾巴时，她的父亲Richard Forster33岁，母亲Elizabeth De Buckton28岁。她于1424年与Sir John Knight在英国史洛普爾史福斯波利结婚。他们至少是2个儿子的父母。她去世于1507年6月19日在英国越可爾克雷文享年107岁。"},"hr":{"1400–19 June 1507":"1400.–19. lipnja 1507.","1400–1507":"1400.–1507","1400–1491":"1400.–1491.","1420–1499":"1420.–1499.","1427–1516":"1427.–1516","1368–Male":"1368–preminuo","1372–1450":"1372–1450.","1450":"1450.","1372":"1372","1491":"1491.","1424":"1424.","1368":"1368","1400":"1400.","1499":"1499.","1455":"1455","1420":"1420.","19 June 1507":"19. lipnja 1507.","1507":"1507","1516":"1516","1427":"1427.","Craven District, North Yorkshire, England":"Craven, Yorkshire, England","Castle Pulverbatch, Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England":"Castle-Pulverbatch, Shropshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Northamptonshire, England":"Northamptonshire, England","Castle-Pulverbatch, Shropshire, England":"Castle-Pulverbatch, Shropshire, England","Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England":"Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England"},"cs":{"1400–19 June 1507":"1400–19. června 1507","1400–1507":"1400–1507","1400–1491":"1400–1491","1420–1499":"1420–1499","1427–1516"